salat-responds-performance\/","url_meta":{"origin":11888,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The prayer responds to good or poor performance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen a man prays, performs ablution well, and perfects its bowing and prostration, the prayer says: May Allah preserve you as you have preserved me! When he performs his bowing poorly, neither perfecting its bowing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3896,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/29\/subhan-ruku-dua-sujud\/","url_meta":{"origin":11888,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Glorify Allah in bowing, supplicate in prostration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO people, there are no more glad tidings of prophecy except righteous dreams seen by a Muslim, or he is made to see. Verily, I have been prohibited from reciting the Quran while bowing or prostrating\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33032,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/what-to-say-ruku-sujud\/","url_meta":{"origin":11888,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: What to say when bowing, prostrating in prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","da